        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer576262262" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11619964942369183555">Liked it, but not as inspiring a read as Being Happy - which I read as a depressed teen. I don&apos;t know if circumstances and youth made Matthews seem wise and profound back then. Now I&apos;m older and have been to several motivational courses so the contents of Follow Your Heart mostly feel like cliches.</span>
  <span id="freeText11619964942369183555" style="display:none">Liked it, but not as inspiring a read as Being Happy - which I read as a depressed teen. I don't know if circumstances and youth made Matthews seem wise and profound back then. Now I'm older and have been to several motivational courses so the contents of Follow Your Heart mostly feel like cliches.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11619964942369183555" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


